snippet.title: Actress Amber Heard leaves Monkia Chiang with a girlfriend possibly platonic after
snippet.description: Actress Amber Heard leaves Monkia Chiang with a girlfriend possibly platonic after shopping on Los Angeles Robertson Boulevard laden with shopping bags. She is wearing her hair tied up in a high ponytail and smart black trousers with a stylish beige jacket. Her blonde friend hurries past her to open the front and back doors of her parked car so Amber can load her spends into the back before jumping into the passenger seat. She says nothing to the photographers and makes no answer to an innocent question about what designer she was wearing that day.
